{"tid":423180,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PC] 上古卷軸集中討論區 19 TESO 機已爆","createTime":"2017-10-03T16:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T17:14:20.000Z","uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ffac6bc8e89b7523d38ac69eb50a76ce6aff3be","tid":423180,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71e9df63e09d614e849781765a5fd22a0b63de5","tid":423180,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開post 唔quote 圖"},{"pid":"f70a19335482d7a87630ca35ccf0cd1082ae4cbb","tid":423180,"uid":117760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1467b3872086f166aad36928465ba3313665102f","tid":423180,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開post 唔quote 圖</blockquote><br />\n用緊電話呀，你搞得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為上個post 爆左冇位放link，驚大家失散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e02d59e1738ffdfe99f4f1e027fdb01b6f44ff","tid":423180,"uid":36087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">喺買之前 你要搞清楚一樣野</span></span><br />\n如果追求穩定或者只係玩ENB&gt;重制版<br />\n如果想玩mod(例如<span style=\"color: red;\">sexlab</span>)&gt;原版(原版steam已經絕版要另外上網買Key)<br />\n再詳細啲:<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=2526&amp;page=&amp;snA=32572&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D2526%26page%3D%26snA%3D32572%26last%3D&d=Nir3tYOHphhhp6JQHhB5ANtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=17588435\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=2526&amp;page=&amp;snA=32572&amp;last=</a><br />\n[quote][新手教學] 一開波我個人會先搞o黎三樣 <br />\n<br />\n1. 裝 SKSE (Current build 1.7.3) <br />\n<a href=\"http://skse.silverlock.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fskse.silverlock.org&d=Nir3tYOHphhhp6JQHhB5ANtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=8eb3ca84\" target=\"_blank\">http://skse.silverlock.org</a> <br />\n首先將三個 files copy 去你 skyrim 個 dir (唔係 DATA, 係 TESV.exe 果度) <br />\nskse_1_9_32.dll <br />\nskse_loader.exe <br />\nskse_steam_loader.dll <br />\nok 如果冇問題你以後開 skyrim 係用 skse_loader.exe o黎 START GAME <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 裝 FNIS (第時你 d mods 需要加新 animation 時用到) <br />\nFNIS Behavior V6_3 <br />\n<a href=\"http://nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F11811&d=Nir3tYOHphhhp6JQHhB5ANtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=b9477289\" target=\"_blank\">http://nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11811</a> <br />\n<br />\n3. 裝 SkyUI (以後加 mods 都需要佢介面o黎做 setting) <br />\n<a href=\"http://nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fmods%2F3863&d=Nir3tYOHphhhp6JQHhB5ANtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=75f416b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3863</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三樣搞掂冇問題先開始裝想要既 mods 例如一開始可以先試風景<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上由NEADer巴打提供<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">依個係佢之前高登個名</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"926dd59e3c1c4241c9b01e284d972ec74fa236a5","tid":423180,"uid":117760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"開個真.19 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a27a483bf02f51a7233cb7160c